title: The Dyson Difference - Official Dyson Video
description: The Dyson Difference - Official Dyson Video
transcripts: The first time we used our Dyson vacuum it was more like an aha moment, like this is what it's supposed to be like when we're vacuuming. I actually thought that I had a clean home with clean floors and it was astonishing the amount of stuff that my Dyson vacuum picked up that my old vacuum had left behind. The designs for the Dyson vacuum is absolutely spot on. The ball design, it feels just a little bit like dancing just a little bit. I have a little wiggle that I like to do when I use my Dyson vacuum. And that makes you feel a little cooler right. The Dyson vacuum cleaner really makes a difference in my home. I love it I absolutely love it. This is my go to product for as long as Dyson manufactures this, I will be buying it.
